Job Description:
Your main tasks will be to:
Support collaborative research projects with desk research, data mining and software developments aspects;
Develop and support efforts to study inputs, outputs and throughputs of research processes the processes, taking a multifaceted and multidisciplinary approach;
Assess and evaluate existing indicators of research reproducibility and research impact, to help develop solutions for our customers to improve and optimize that impact
Work on projects involving a data science/NLP/Machine Learning approach, eg. developing methodologies for detecting compliance with e.g. clinical reporting guidelines in medical journal articles, possibly in collaboration with academic partners;

